OL,3,CDrug shortages 'beyond critical' amid
OL,4,Cpersisting pharmacy supply issues
OL,6,FAs the drug supply "crisis" in England
OL,7,Fcontinues, patients are being forced
OL,8,Fto ration their medication, with
OL,9,Fpharmacy shortages now a daily
OL,10,Foccurrence.
OL,12,FA new survey reveals that patients are
OL,13,Fhaving to play "pharmacy bingo" -
OL,14,Ftravelling from shop to shop to find
OL,15,Fstock - amid worsening .
OL,17,FTreatments for ADHD, diabetes, and
OL,18,Fepilepsy are among those worse
OL,19,Faffected, according to trade body
OL,20,FCommunity Pharmacy England.
