OL,3,CDrug shortages 'beyond critical' amid
OL,4,Cpersisting pharmacy supply issues
OL,6,F"The medicine supply challenges being
OL,7,Ffaced by community pharmacies and
OL,8,Ftheir patients are beyond critical,"
OL,9,Fthe body's chief executive, Janet
OL,10,FMorrison, said.
OL,12,F"We've been warning for some time that
OL,13,Fthese issues must be resolved, and
OL,14,Fthis evidence provides yet another
OL,15,Fstark warning which must not be
OL,16,Fignored."
OL,18,FThe study of more than 6,000 patients
OL,19,Fand 2,000 staff found shortages are
OL,20,F"wreaking havoc" on patients.
