OL,3,CDrug shortages 'beyond critical' amid
OL,4,Cpersisting pharmacy supply issues
OL,6,FAlmost all (97%) of said their
OL,7,Fpatients are inconvenienced by supply
OL,8,Fissues, while 79% said patient health
OL,9,Fwas at risk.
OL,11,FResearchers warned that alongside
OL,12,Fstress and inconvenience, lack of
OL,13,Faccess to medication can lead to
OL,14,Fserious health consequences, even
OL,15,Fleaving patients needing to visit A&E.
OL,17,FWilliam Pett, Head of Policy at
OL,18,FHealthwatch England, said medicine
OL,19,Fsupply is an "ongoing issue" that
OL,20,F"continues to wreak havoc on patients".
