OL,3,CDrug shortages 'beyond critical' amid
OL,4,Cpersisting pharmacy supply issues
OL,6,FHe said Healthwatch is calling for a
OL,7,Freview of the medicine supply chain,
OL,8,Fand for pharmacists to "be given
OL,9,Fflexibility to make changes to
OL,10,Fmedicines they dispense in
OL,11,Fcollaboration with patients".
OL,13,FThe National Pharmacy Association also
OL,14,Fcalled for the government to fix the
OL,15,FUK's "fragile" supply system.
OL,17,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,18,Fspokesperson said: "Supply issues can
OL,19,Farise for a wide range of reasons and
OL,20,Fare not specific to the UK.
